---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "About | Port Credit Cleaning"
description: "Port Credit Cleaning is a locally-owned, owner-operated cleaning team serving Port Credit and South Mississauga with honest, dependable house cleaning."
---

{# ── HERO ── #}
<section class="bg-navy py-16 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sand text-[12.5px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.13em] mb-4">About us</p>
      <h1 class="font-display font-extrabold text-white text-[42px] md:text-[48px] leading-[1.07] tracking-[-0.022em] mb-5">A small, local cleaning team you can trust</h1>
      <p class="text-[#A8BDD0] text-[18px] leading-relaxed">Port Credit Cleaning is a small, owner-operated business built on a simple idea: dependable cleaning from a team that genuinely cares about your home.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="rounded-[20px] overflow-hidden w-full aspect-square max-w-[380px] mx-auto md:mx-0">
      {% image "/img/pexels-artbovich-6538930.jpg", "Bright, finished condo living room in Port Credit", "w-full h-full object-cover", "(min-width: 768px) 380px, 100vw" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── STORY ── #}
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-[840px] mx-auto px-8">
    <p class="text-teal text-[12.5px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.13em] mb-3">Our story</p>
    <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-navy text-[36px] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.022em] mb-8">Local roots, and a higher standard of clean</h2>
    <div class="space-y-5 text-[17px] text-[#4A5568] leading-[1.7]">
      <p>Port Credit Cleaning started right here on the lakeshore with a simple goal: bring a genuinely dependable cleaning service to the neighbourhood, without the rotating crews and call-center feel of the big franchises.</p>
      <p>We're a small, local team — not a faceless franchise — so we get to know each home and the people in it. That's how we make sure a space feels right for you, not just clean.</p>
      <p>Whether it's a weekly clean for a busy family, a deep clean before guests arrive, or a move-out reset, our commitment is the same: show up on time, pay attention to the details, and leave your home feeling genuinely cared for.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ── VALUES ── #}
<section class="py-16 bg-surface">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-7">
    {% set values = [
      ["Locally rooted", "Born and based in Port Credit. Your community is my community."],
      ["Detail-obsessed", "A consistent checklist every visit, so nothing slips through the cracks."],
      ["Always reliable", "On time, every time — and easy to reach when plans change."]
    ] %}
    {% for v in values %}
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[16px] p-7" style="box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(23,50,77,.05);">
      <div class="w-11 h-11 bg-teal-tint rounded-[12px] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" stroke="#5AA7A7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="9"/>
          <polyline points="9 11 11 13 15 9"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-navy text-[18px] mb-2">{{ v[0] }}</h3>
      <p class="text-[#4A5568] text-[15px] leading-relaxed">{{ v[1] }}</p>
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>

{# ── COMPACT QUOTE BAND ── #}
<section class="py-16 bg-navy">
  <div class="max-w-[1180px] mx-auto px-8 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
    <div>
      <p class="text-sand text-[12.5px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.13em] mb-3">Free quote</p>
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold text-white text-[32px] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.022em] mb-4">Let's get your home on the schedule</h2>
      <p class="text-[#A8BDD0] text-[17px] leading-relaxed mb-6">Send a few details and we'll get back to you the same day with honest pricing.</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-white/10 rounded-[10px] flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none" stroke="#5AA7A7" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.6 1.18h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l.91-.91a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21.73 16.92z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[12px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-[#5A7290]">Call or text</p>
          <a href="{{ site.phoneTel }}" class="text-white font-semibold text-[15px] hover:text-teal transition-colors duration-150">{{ site.phone }}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[16px] p-7">
      {% set formType = "compact" %}
      {% include "partials/quote-form.njk" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
